 this she is the 25th MBGN since the pargent kicked off 25 years ago. May 7, 2012 In "Entertainment" A new most beautiful girl in Nigeria is billed to emerge today as Silverbird Group, organisers of the Most Beautiful Girl in Nigeria (MBGN), holds the 25th edition of the beauty pageant. The new beauty queen will represent Nigeria at all international pageants, including the Miss World. May 5, 2012 In "Showtime People"